history.text: Good evening. Have you seen this movie?
I have seen this movie.
Keanu Reeves is a good action star.
Yes he is!  I don't believe that I have actually seen this one though.  Is it a good suspense thriller?
It is a great action thriller. it is the kind of movie that you just sit back and enjoy.
The plot may be basic, but the action more than makes up for it.
I tend to like those..  It seems as though his role is that of an ex-hitman.  Could u tell me a little more about it?  Is it something that children should clearly not watch?
This definitely not a children's movie. It has a lot of brutal violence in it.
Ok.  That is good to know!  In your own opinion, what other movie does it resemble?  Or is it something of its own?
I think that it resembles a lot of Jason Stathem films.
It says that his wife is deceased, does it go into detail as to why or how it happened?
It sadly was not stated how or why his wife died.
I didn't know if it was part of the plot or anything.  I tend to lean towards movies that have a strong beginning to keep my attention thru the whole thing.  Does it start off slow or anything?
I would say that it does start off a bit slow, but it is not too bad in that regard. It really ramps up from the middle until the end of the movie.
Ok!  What other features of this movie did u like?
I like the use of colors and cinematography. The movie has a colorful, saturated look to it that keeps your attention.
The acting is also surprisingly strong for the type of movie this is.
I like good movie features like that.  Could u tell me a bit more about where it takes place?  Any other well known actors/actress in it?
Well, there's Keanu Reeves, who is the biggest known star. There is also Alfie Allen from Game of Thrones fame. The location is from multiple places.
I cannot remember the specific places though.
Ok!  Seems like a very interesting movie!
It is. I hope you enjoy it.
I am sure it will be added to something I do watch, even if it is a bit of an older movie!  Looks like the scoring on it seems pretty good.  I am all about good reviews!
I really am all about a good, suspense/action movie!
I am too.
The movie also has some great scenes.
The club scene was great.
Weird thing is, I am all about a great hitman movie!   Club scene?  I assume lots of gunfire??
Yeah, the scene has a strong Hitman vibe to it.
Expect Keanu is far less stealthy
Is the ending good or one of those that will take you by surprise and wishing there was more?
The ending feels a bit undercooked compared to the middle of the movie, which is my biggest complaint with the movie.
My all time favorite Keanu Reeves movie is still Speed!
I get a bit frustrated with terrible endings!
me too
